                <ddattrs:ShortDescription>Database about nationally designated areas, which includes nature protection sites such as national parks and nature reserves but also other designated areas providing durable protection for flora and fauna, e.g. through management schemes.</ddattrs:ShortDescription>
                <ddattrs:Methodology>The available CDDA data delivered earlier to EEA are provided in a template based on these Data dictionary definitions. Reporters are asked to review and update the data, providing the information on the current situation of the designated areas in their countries. &#13;
